    <licence>GFDL</licence>
    <name>Fedy</name>
    <summary>Install codecs, software, and more...</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
        Fedy lets you install multimedia codecs and additional software that
        Fedora doesn't want to ship, like mp3 support, Adobe Flash, Oracle Java
        etc., and much more with just a few clicks.
        </p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Simple and easy to use GUI</li>
            <li>Always installs latest versions of software</li>
            <li>Saves downloaded files for later use</li>
            <li>Can be run from the command line</li>
            <li>Extensible with plugins</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
